{"id":22,"date":"2008-06-26T14:43:59","date_gmt":"2008-06-26T14:43:59","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.synres.org\/?page_id=8"},"modified":"2024-04-09T10:03:30","modified_gmt":"2024-04-09T14:03:30","slug":"careers","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/mipath.org\/careers\/","title":{"rendered":"Careers"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https:\/\/recruitingbypaycor.com\/career\/CareerHome.action?clientId=8a7883d08d19fedb018d5d060b223293&amp;specialization=\">Click here to apply online<\/a><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Pathlight Community Services is committed to our charitable purpose of providing psychosocial rehabilitation services to our community by manifesting concern, sensitivity, patience and human kindness for consumers, their needs, preferences and choices. We succeed in keeping the welfare and best interests of our consumers as our primary concern through development and maintenance of programming that encourages an individual\u2019s strengths, abilities and personality and addresses the needs of the whole person.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Our employees are our greatest assets. They recognize and accept their role as stewards, accept professional responsibility for the services provided and take steps to provide for the growth and development of the agency and the services it offers the community.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The care of vulnerable or dependent individuals entails an enormous grant and acceptance of trust as well as a profound amount of responsibility for ensuring the well-being and safety of another human life. For the right person, this job can become a career, offering days that are both meaningful and emotionally gratifying. It is the perfect entry into nursing, occupational therapy, teaching, psychology or social work.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Pathlight Community Services realizes that the quality of care received by our consumers is dependent on the health and well-being of the people who care for them. In addition to the emotional gratification obtained from employment at Pathlight Community Services, we offer many perks to help meet the practical, daily needs of our employees<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Intensive paid training <\/strong>\u2013 This training has a flexible schedule to accommodate scheduling conflicts.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Flexible work schedules <\/strong>\u2013 With many programs requiring 24-hour staffing, we are able to offer around-the-clock shifts and have employment schedules that range from occasional to full-time schedules.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Competitive pay rates<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Benefit packages <\/strong>\u2013 Include health, dental and life insurance, paid time off, and 401k retirement plan.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Long-term employment<strong>&nbsp;<\/strong><\/strong>\u2013 Our flexibility, in combination with the benefit packages and advancement opportunities, enables our staff not only to have a job but plan for a career at Pathlight Community Services.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Advancement opportunities<strong><strong>&nbsp;<\/strong><\/strong><\/strong>\u2013 Several levels of management responsibility allow staff opportunities for promotions.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Challenging and stimulating work<br><\/strong><br><strong>Employee involvement <\/strong>\u2013 Opportunities such as the Grievance Committee, Camp, and Open Door Policy encourage employees to participate in decisions affecting them and their daily professional responsibilities.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Variety of locations and job duties<strong>&nbsp;<\/strong><\/strong>\u2013<a href=\"https:\/\/drive.google.com\/file\/d\/13sAb0FYQhpLM-IieZKKTivoaflYdo57i\/view?usp=sharing\">&nbsp;<strong>Direct Care Worker job description (PDF)&nbsp;<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><br>Pathlight Community Services is an equal opportunity employer. Pathlight Community Services does not unlawfully discriminate on the basis of race, color, sex, (including pregnancy, childbirth, or related medical condi